Interface Propagation

    public interface Propagation
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Propagation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Prob
    • Delay
    • Base Connector
    • Base Instance Specification
    • Base Comment
